  "instructions": [
    "Heat oil in a large saucepan over medium heat.",
    "Add onion and cook until translucent, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add ginger and garlic and cook for another minute.",
    "Add shrimp and cook until pink, about 2-3 minutes.",
    "Add shrimp stock, coconut milk, tomato puree, curry powder, cumin, coriander, salt, and cayenne pepper.",
    "Stir well and bring to a boil.",
    "Reduce heat to low and simmer for 10-15 minutes or until the sauce has thickened.",
    "Stir in cilantro and cook for another minute.",
    "Serve hot over basmati rice or with naan bread."
